gov.usgs.anss.edgemom

Class Q680Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • gov.usgs.anss.edgethread.EdgeThread
        • gov.usgs.anss.edgemom.Q680Manager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public final class Q680Manager
extends EdgeThread
    This is a template for an EdgeThread (one that can be run by EdgeMom). It includes a timeout on the run() and a registered shutdown handler. Since Q680 and Q730s are no longer in use, this is likely obsolete. At a minimum Q680Manager should be replaced to the new class And GSNM replaces with a short hand for the class. (ETT??).
